    • Constructor Detail

      • AbstractDisplayProperty

        protected AbstractDisplayProperty(String displayKey,
                                  Property.Type type,
                                  String name,
                                  DisplayProperty.Widget widget,
                                  String defaultDescription,
                                  boolean sensitive,
                                  boolean hidden)
        Creates an abstract display property with the specified parameters.
        Parameters:
        displayKey - the display key
        type - the type of the display property, or null to use the default type of STRING
        name - the default human-readable name of the display property, for error messages and labels, used when a localized name cannot be found, or null to use the display key
        widget - the widget used to display values of the property, or null to use the default TEXT widget
        defaultDescription - the default human-readable description of the display property, used when a localized description cannot be found
        sensitive - whether the display property contains sensitive information
        hidden - whether the display property should be hidden from the user interface
